      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in genuinely good condition and has been consistently maintained over the years. The engine runs strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, providing a very reliable and comfortable driving experience. While there are minor signs of normal use consistent with its age, the interior remains clean and all major systems are fully operational. It\u2019s a solid, well-cared-for car that is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
