    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for a daily driver. Mechanically, it has been well-maintained with regular oil changes and recent brake service, ensuring it runs smoothly. However, the exterior shows its age with some clear coat peeling on the trunk, a few minor parking lot dings, and visible scuffing on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is clean but shows some thinning on the driver's seat bolster and a small crack in the dashboard plastics. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that is ready for many more miles, even if it isn't a showpiece.",
