    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unparalleled distinction. This specimen remains in an immaculate state, reflecting a standard of preservation rarely encountered in the secondary market. Every component, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, adheres to the highest benchmarks of automotive excellence. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a definitive acquisition. We invite serious inquiries to experience this peerless example firsthand.",
      "price": 48500.0,
